; Native MongoDB backend: a thin Fennec_pulse.Backend.S adapter over the ported driver layer
; (fennec-mongo.driver — Client/Collection/Live), so the whole reactive / DDP / realtime stack runs
; over a real mongod UNCHANGED (same seam Minimongo implements in memory). observe_changes is real
; change streams (Live), not polling. Native only (the driver links the C FFI + Eio) — the
; browser/SSR use fennec.pulse with the in-memory backend instead.
(library
 (name fennec_pulse_mongo)
 (public_name fennec.pulse.mongo)
 (libraries fennec.pulse fennec-mongo.driver fennec-mongo.ffi fennec-mongo.bson fennec-mongo.query eio))
